        <options>
            <option letter="a">To establish an eight-hour workday</option>
            <option letter="b">To prevent immigration</option>
            <option letter="c">To support business owners</option>
            <option letter="d">To promote racial segregation</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The National Labor Union, founded in 1866, focused primarily on achieving an eight-hour workday for American workers through political action.</explanation>
