    <question number="24">
        <prompt>How did the "rebate" system affect railroad competition?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Gave large shippers unfair advantages</option>
            <option letter="b">Reduced shipping costs for all</option>
            <option letter="c">Improved railroad efficiency</option>
            <option letter="d">Protected small businesses</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The rebate system gave secret discounts to large shippers, allowing big businesses to undercut competitors and contributing to the formation of monopolies.</explanation>
